rows.label: qst200827_msg0001
rows.name:
There's no way for you to
win, so just give up!

rows.label: qst200827_msg0002
rows.name: We don't have any secret information!

rows.label: qst200827_msg0004
rows.name: I said I had a plan, didn't I?

rows.label: qst200827_msg0005
rows.name:
I know how important those stupid
Saffronia trees are to you...

rows.label: qst200827_msg0006
rows.name:
So I decided I'll burn
them bit by bit until you
hand over the documents.

rows.label: qst200827_msg0010
rows.name:
It seems like we've finally
gained the upper hand...

rows.label: qst200827_msg0011
rows.name:
See that? We're starting
with three of 'em. I let my
colleagues do the honors.

rows.label: qst200827_msg0012
rows.name:
Give me the documents! Or
should I set some more fires?

rows.label: qst200827_msg0013
rows.name: I keep telling you I don't have any!

rows.label: qst200827_msg0014
rows.name:
Guys, there's no use talking
with them! Quickly, let's
put out the fires!

rows.label: qst200827_msg0016
rows.name:
Wouldn't it be quicker to just
give up the documents...?

rows.label: qst200827_msg0017
rows.name:
Well, it's your choice! I'll be waiting
till you change your minds... And
burning trees to pass the time!
